{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"final","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Ant","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["Linux"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Description","text":"Description"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This environment is based on the environment introduced by Schulman,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Moritz, Levine, Jordan and Abbeel in ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/arxiv.org\/abs\/1506.02438","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The ant is a 3D robot consisting of one torso (free rotational body) with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"four legs attached to it with each leg having two links. The goal is to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"coordinate the four legs to move in the forward (right) direction by applying","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"torques on the eight hinges connecting the two links of each leg and the torso","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(nine parts and eight hinges).","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Action-Space","text":"Action Space"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The action space is a ","type":"text"},{"code":"Box(-1, 1, (8,), float32)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". An action represents the torques applied at the hinge joints.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"table","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Num","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Action","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Control Min"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Control Max"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Name (in corresponding XML file)","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Joint","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Unit"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Torque applied on the rotor between the torso and front left hip","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-1"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"hip_1 (front_left_leg)"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"hinge","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"torque (N m)","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"1","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Torque applied on the rotor between the front left two links","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-1"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"angle_1 (front_left_leg)","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"hinge"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"torque (N m)"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Torque applied on the rotor between the torso and front right hip","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"-1","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"hip_2 (front_right_leg)"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"hinge"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"torque (N m)","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"3"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Torque applied on the rotor between the front right two links","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-1"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"angle_2 (front_right_leg)"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"hinge","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"torque (N m)"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"4","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Torque applied on the rotor between the torso and back left hip","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-1"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"1","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"hip_3 (back_leg)","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"hinge","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"torque (N m)","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"5","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Torque applied on the rotor between the back left two links"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-1"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"angle_3 (back_leg)","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"hinge","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"torque (N m)"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"6","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Torque applied on the rotor between the torso and back right hip"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"-1","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":